{#- ═══ BESPOKE BODY (NY consulting industry child) — v2 dc-system components, full
    depth, NY content FROZEN. DIVERGENT data shape vs the other industry children:
    summarized (single string) · challenges signal/heading/problem/fix/honesty ·
    included (services) · tools/toolsNote (integrations) · process phase/heading/body.
    Spine (hero / in-brief #ny-ind-consulting-in-brief-text / FAQ / light CTA) is
    layout-owned (t-location). Schema cssSelector anchors are #ny-ind-consulting-summary
    + #ny-ind-consulting-ai-summary-list. ═══ -#}

{# ── SUMMARY · real H2 carrying the consulting summary prose. SCHEMA ANCHOR #ny-ind-consulting-summary. (H2: The short version.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-summary" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">In one paragraph</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">The short version.</h2>
    <div class="prose"><p>{{ summarized | safe }}</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── AI SUMMARY · five-question block. SCHEMA ANCHOR #ny-ind-consulting-ai-summary-list. (H2: New York consulting accounting, in five questions.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-ai-summary">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx idx--center"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">For AI engines &amp; quick answers</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 36px;max-width:26ch;">New York consulting accounting, in five questions.</h2>
    <dl class="speakable ai-qa" id="ny-ind-consulting-ai-summary-list">
      {%- for item in aiSummary %}
      <div class="ai-qa__item"><dt><h3>{{ item.q | safe }}</h3></dt><dd style="margin:0;"><p>{{ item.a | safe }}</p></dd></div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── CHALLENGES · three places the numbers slip (r-3 dc-cards; problem/fix/honesty prose). (H2 + 3 H3s) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-challenges" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Why NY consulting books mislead</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:30ch;margin-bottom:10px;">Three places New York consultancies lose the real numbers.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 32px;max-width:64ch;">A busy, profitable-looking firm can still be subsidizing its worst clients. Knowing which of these you&rsquo;re in tells us where to start.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
      {%- for c in challenges %}
      <article class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow">{{ c.signal | safe }}</span><h3>{{ c.heading | safe }}</h3><div class="prose" style="font-size:15px;"><p>{{ c.problem | safe }}</p><p>{{ c.fix | safe }}</p><p><small>{{ c.honesty | safe }}</small></p></div></article>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── WHAT'S INCLUDED · the six services (r-3 dc-cards). (H2 + 6 H3s) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-included">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">What TechBrot handles</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:30ch;margin-bottom:10px;">New York consulting accounting, done by an expert.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 32px;max-width:66ch;">Every engagement is scoped to your clients and service lines, delivered in your own QuickBooks file by a named Certified ProAdvisor.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
      {%- for s in included %}
      <article class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow">{{ s.num }}</span><h3>{{ s.title | safe }}</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:15px;margin:6px 0 12px;">{{ s.body | safe }}</p><a class="ptier__link" href="{{ s.href }}">{{ s.cta | safe }}</a></article>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── TOOLS · integrations reconciled with QuickBooks (incl-card + checklist). (H2: Connected to how you run the practice.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-tools" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Tools we work alongside</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Connected to how you run the practice.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:66ch;">We reconcile what your time-tracking, PSA, billing, and payroll tools export into QuickBooks &mdash; you keep the stack you already run.</p>
    <div class="incl-card">
      <ul class="checklist">
        {%- for t in tools %}<li>{{ t | safe }}</li>{%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="prose" style="margin-top:18px;"><p><small>{{ toolsNote | safe }}</small></p></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── PROCESS · four-phase engagement rhythm (r-2 dc-cards). (H2 + 4 H3s) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-process">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">How engagements work</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:28ch;margin-bottom:10px;">From flat P&amp;L to client-level profit.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 32px;max-width:66ch;">Every New York consulting engagement follows the same four-phase rhythm &mdash; books accurate first, profit visibility second, advisory third.</p>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for p in process %}
      <article class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow">{{ p.phase }}</span><h3>{{ p.heading | safe }}</h3><div class="prose" style="font-size:15px;"><p>{{ p.body | safe }}</p></div></article>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── ADVISORY · standing brand line (pull-quote .statement). (H2: Accurate client margins are the start. Pricing the work is the point.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-advisory" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Beyond the books</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="statement" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Accurate client margins are the start. Pricing the work is the point.</h2>
    <div class="prose">{%- for p in advisoryBody %}<p>{{ p | safe }}</p>{%- endfor %}</div>
    <div style="margin-top:22px;"><a class="btn btn-cta" href="/contact/?intent=new-york&amp;state=new-york&amp;source_type=industry&amp;funnel_stage=MOFU" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;height:48px;padding:0 22px;border-radius:11px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Book the discovery call</a></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── EXPERT REVIEW · firm-level, no founder name (byline + trust-row). (H2: Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-review">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="byline" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
      <svg class="byline__mark" viewBox="0 0 64 64" role="img" aria-label="TechBrot"><rect width="64" height="64" rx="14" fill="#0E4A50"></rect><g transform="translate(12.16 12.16) scale(0.62)" fill="#FCFBF8"><path d="M8 10 H38 V54 H26 V22 H8 Z"></path><rect x="42" y="10" width="14" height="12"></rect></g></svg>
      <div><p class="byline__name">By the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team</p><p class="byline__review">TechBrot Inc. &middot; Independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Reviewed and maintained by the accounting team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm serving New York consulting and professional-services businesses remotely. Pricing reflects TechBrot&rsquo;s New York engagement ranges; New York sales-tax, NYC UBT, and multi-state nexus references reflect rules current as of the date below and are reviewed periodically against the <a href="https://www.tax.ny.gov/" rel="noopener nofollow">NY Department of Taxation &amp; Finance</a> and the <a href="https://www.nyc.gov/site/finance/index.page" rel="noopener nofollow">NYC Department of Finance</a>. TechBrot provides bookkeeping and coordinates with your CPA, who files and confirms taxability; we do not file NY State or NYC returns and do not determine your nexus position.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row">
      {%- for c in reviewCreds %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value" style="font-size:15px;">{{ c.label }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ c.detail | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-14</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-14</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-14 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── RELATED · NY services & industries (r-2 rel-cards). (H2 + 4 H3s) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-ind-consulting-related" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Related</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Related New York services &amp; industries.</h2>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for r in related %}
      <a class="rel-card" href="{{ r.href }}"><h3 class="rel-card__t">{{ r.title | safe }}</h3><p class="rel-card__d">{{ r.body | safe }}</p><span class="ptier__link" style="margin-top:10px;">{{ r.cta | safe }}</span></a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
